## 💡 BONUS: Creating Gates from NAND

**Using only NAND gates:**

```
NOT A = A NAND A
A AND B = (A NAND B) NAND (A NAND B)
A OR B = (A NAND A) NAND (B NAND B)
```

**Why is this asked?** Proves NAND is universal!

